BM   hmmbuild  -o /dev/null HMM SEED
SM   hmmsearch -Z 90746521 --cpu 8 -E 1000 HMM pfamseq
TP   Family
CL   CL0183
CC   This entry represents a C-terminal region (approximately 565-730
CC   residues) found in two-component system chemotaxis proteins with
CC   methyltransferase (CheR) and methylesterase (CheB) activity. These
CC   proteins contain CheB_methylest, CheR_N, CheR and PAS domains and are
CC   involved in bacterial chemotaxis signalling. The family belongs to
CC   clan CL0183. It is found in Thermodesulfobacteriota (Desulfovibrionia,
CC   Desulfovibrionales), Pseudomonadota, Bacillota (Bacilli, Bacillales,
CC   Paenibacillaceae, Paenibacillus, Clostridia) and Bacteroidota
CC   (Cytophagia, Cytophagales, Hymenobacteraceae, Pontibacter).
